div.p:
Now we have new opportunity to strengthen the relationship between UCSY and Keio University. UCSY and Keio University, wishing to promote cooperation between the two institutions in education and in academic research, and agree to the following things:


to exchange scientific information in the form of publications, instruction materials and other results of teaching and research;

to support mutual visits by faculty members and researchers;

to exchange graduate and/or undergraduate students;

to develop joint research activities;

to invite each other to participate in seminars and conferences organized by the respective institutions.
